<h1>Introduction</h1>
<h2>Welcome to Conquer Space!</h2>
</div>
<div>
<p>You are in control of a civilization of a planet. You are to lead them to explore and expand in the galaxy, and lead your civilization to prosperity.</p>
<p>However, you are not alone. There are also other civilizations in the galaxy, who also want to do the same.</p>
<p>Some are violent, others are peaceful. You can choose too, to meet them with violence or peace.</p>
<p>Forge alliances for the advancement of all civilizations, scientific, culturally, and socially. Or, wage war against invaders who only see you as a resource, to protect your people.</p>
<p>Remember your goal is to: <b>Conquer Space!</b></p>
